WEBVTT

00:00:10.355 --> 00:00:11.125
Hey.

00:00:11.185 --> 00:00:11.965
Do you know each other?

00:00:12.025 --> 00:00:13.905
She’s the bakery owner you’re so obsessed with.

00:00:14.025 --> 00:00:16.305
Instructor, please train my daughter well.

00:00:16.393 --> 00:00:17.185
No favoritism.

00:00:17.265 --> 00:00:18.105
No special treatment.

00:00:18.425 --> 00:00:20.465
Wrong is wrong. Fill in whatever she lacks.

00:00:20.598 --> 00:00:22.285
I want my daughter to be a survivor.

00:00:22.385 --> 00:00:23.465
And to be able to stand on her own.

00:00:23.885 --> 00:00:25.291
It's only the first day.

00:00:25.585 --> 00:00:27.545
Don't you want to stay and
fight just a little longer?

00:00:27.985 --> 00:00:28.905
Stay and prove.

00:00:28.985 --> 00:00:31.025
Show the people who think you've already given up

00:00:31.145 --> 00:00:33.505
that you aren't as weak as they thought.

00:00:33.625 --> 00:00:35.265
Your daughter makes such delicious cakes.

00:00:35.625 --> 00:00:37.044
Why did you let her become a police?

00:01:18.985 --> 00:01:19.785
Why...

00:01:21.273 --> 00:01:22.894
Your heart is beating so fast.

00:02:31.145 --> 00:02:31.825
It's okay.

00:04:10.025 --> 00:04:13.105
Without a brooch, just tie
a knot at the corner like this.

00:04:13.625 --> 00:04:16.505
Then, tuck in all four corners neatly

00:04:16.745 --> 00:04:18.345
Pull it as tight as possible.

00:04:18.825 --> 00:04:20.465
And then, tuck in the edges along the sides.

00:04:21.085 --> 00:04:21.905
Like this.

00:04:24.345 --> 00:04:25.391
And then, take the blanket.

00:04:26.825 --> 00:04:28.863
Then, you double-check everything.

00:04:30.225 --> 00:04:30.985
Done.

00:04:35.825 --> 00:04:37.287
Why is this so complicated?

00:04:37.505 --> 00:04:39.145
It's just for a few hours of sleep anyway.

00:04:42.465 --> 00:04:44.091
I'll make the bed for you this time

00:04:45.265 --> 00:04:46.692
Because if I let you do it yourself.

00:04:47.025 --> 00:04:48.585
We definitely won't make it to the assembly on time.

00:04:49.905 --> 00:04:50.331
Oh.

00:04:51.847 --> 00:04:53.265
I thought you were worried about me.

00:04:53.425 --> 00:04:54.313
Turns out.

00:04:54.465 --> 00:04:55.985
You’re just afraid of
getting punished because of me.

00:05:07.534 --> 00:05:09.242
Who would ever worry about a naughty kid like you?

00:05:42.585 --> 00:05:43.412
Anyway...

00:05:43.924 --> 00:05:45.019
Let's practice this evening.

00:05:45.665 --> 00:05:46.825
Then tomorrow, you’ll do it on your own.

00:05:57.905 --> 00:05:59.145
Before we begin today's training,

00:06:00.145 --> 00:06:01.345
I have a question to ask.

00:06:03.545 --> 00:06:04.578
Who broke the rules last night?

00:06:06.539 --> 00:06:07.802
Sneaking in for a shower

00:06:08.425 --> 00:06:09.732
during unauthorized hours.

00:06:12.705 --> 00:06:13.858
Step forward, right now!

00:06:15.625 --> 00:06:18.305
Before I have someone check the CCTV footage.

00:06:47.585 --> 00:06:48.385
Who else?

00:06:49.825 --> 00:06:50.625
No one else, sir.

00:06:51.265 --> 00:06:52.225
Just me.

00:06:55.865 --> 00:06:56.665
Are you sure?

00:06:58.065 --> 00:06:58.985
Yes, I'm sure.

00:07:04.865 --> 00:07:06.225
Since you've admitted to it.

00:07:07.905 --> 00:07:08.865
After dinner

00:07:09.585 --> 00:07:10.545
report to me.

00:07:11.625 --> 00:07:12.425
Yes, sir.

00:07:15.305 --> 00:07:16.225
Back to your position.

00:07:38.145 --> 00:07:38.945
Hey.

00:07:39.665 --> 00:07:40.825
Why did you do this?

00:07:40.985 --> 00:07:43.385
I’m not okay with you taking the blame for me.

00:07:44.465 --> 00:07:45.985
If I had stopped you from the beginning,

00:07:46.265 --> 00:07:47.545
You wouldn't have taken that shower.

00:07:48.345 --> 00:07:49.665
