00:07:49.745 --> 00:07:51.345
is a violation too.

00:07:54.825 --> 00:07:55.385
Then...

00:07:55.705 --> 00:07:56.825
After target practice,

00:07:57.265 --> 00:07:58.505
I’m going to see the instructor with you.

00:08:00.625 --> 00:08:02.585
Don't make a big deal out of it.

00:08:03.185 --> 00:08:04.585
I'm stronger than you.

00:08:05.318 --> 00:08:06.828
And I'm more used to the system.

00:08:08.505 --> 00:08:09.025
Listen,

00:08:10.105 --> 00:08:11.345
If you feel guilty,

00:08:11.705 --> 00:08:13.265
then just focus on doing a great job.

00:08:14.185 --> 00:08:15.625
Blow that target to pieces.

00:08:20.385 --> 00:08:21.345
This range

00:08:22.385 --> 00:08:24.185
isn't just about hitting the target.

00:08:24.505 --> 00:08:25.665
It’s about focus.

00:08:25.905 --> 00:08:27.225
And self-control.

00:08:27.345 --> 00:08:29.105
To become one with your weapon.

00:08:29.572 --> 00:08:30.585
Before pulling the trigger,

00:08:30.785 --> 00:08:31.638
