00:08:32.745 --> 00:08:35.065
Pick your preferred weapon.

00:09:00.651 --> 00:09:01.437
Back straight.

00:09:04.689 --> 00:09:05.948
Arms out.

00:09:08.372 --> 00:09:09.405
Steady your aim.

00:09:15.185 --> 00:09:16.313
Lower your hands a bit.

00:09:34.825 --> 00:09:35.677
That's it.

