Don't forget to rack the slide.

00:09:48.564 --> 00:09:49.336
Like this.

00:09:52.185 --> 00:09:52.745
Umm.

00:09:54.181 --> 00:09:54.957
Keep your arms straight.

00:10:14.258 --> 00:10:15.211
Whoa!

00:10:16.425 --> 00:10:17.979
How are you such a sharpshooter?

00:10:19.009 --> 00:10:19.555
Hey,

00:10:20.219 --> 00:10:21.127
I thought you were James Bond.

00:10:23.444 --> 00:10:24.226
What about yours?

00:10:24.616 --> 00:10:25.051
How did it go?

