You

00:11:15.858 --> 00:11:17.545
really remind me of my father.

00:11:18.275 --> 00:11:19.044
How so?

00:11:21.336 --> 00:11:22.018
Well...

00:11:23.124 --> 00:11:24.178
I mean that

00:11:24.498 --> 00:11:25.976
most fathers

00:11:26.164 --> 00:11:27.694
don't like their kids eating sweets, right?

00:11:27.945 --> 00:11:28.831
Because they're worried about cavities

00:11:29.065 --> 00:11:29.465
Hmm.

