But my dad.

00:11:31.105 --> 00:11:32.751
He liked me to carry candy to school.

00:11:33.335 --> 00:11:34.626
He said it was to help me stay awake.

00:11:35.145 --> 00:11:35.805
See?

00:11:35.965 --> 00:11:37.026
You're just like him.

00:11:40.105 --> 00:11:40.967
Hey.

00:11:41.665 --> 00:11:42.943
Little one.

00:11:47.785 --> 00:11:48.546
Hurry up!

00:11:48.705 --> 00:11:49.645
We're going to be late!

00:11:52.065 --> 00:11:54.418
The transit period is the most vulnerable phase.

00:11:55.655 --> 00:11:58.150
Assailants often take
this opportunity to surround,

00:11:58.724 --> 00:11:59.590
ambush,

00:12:00.202 --> 00:12:01.329
or plant explosives.

00:12:01.745 --> 00:12:02.838
In this case,

00:12:03.172 --> 00:12:03.840
the driver

00:12:04.098 --> 00:12:05.677
is positioned in the front right seat.

