This simulation

00:12:28.985 --> 00:12:30.705
involves driving through a high-risk area.

00:12:31.336 --> 00:12:32.205
Ambush in progress.

00:12:32.665 --> 00:12:35.105
00 from 31006, reporting Code 30.

00:12:35.185 --> 00:12:37.430
Convoy under fire during VIP transit.

00:12:47.628 --> 00:12:49.158
Shots fired from the rear.

00:12:49.305 --> 00:12:51.218
Roadblock ahead, path is blocked.

00:12:51.812 --> 00:12:53.475
Unable to proceed. Obstruction ahead.

