Wait for reinforcements.

00:13:21.065 --> 00:13:24.305
Reinforcements will pull up to extract

00:13:24.713 --> 00:13:25.906
the VIP immediately.

00:13:26.625 --> 00:13:28.122
- Get in.
- Get in.

00:13:30.171 --> 00:13:31.005
Go.

00:13:41.496 --> 00:13:42.414
Get in.

00:13:44.505 --> 00:13:45.551
Get in.

