Exhausted feels like I just
came back from an actual war zone.

00:14:45.458 --> 00:14:46.769
Will I make it through the afternoon?

00:14:48.981 --> 00:14:50.341
Just have to push through it.

00:14:50.633 --> 00:14:52.018
unless you want to get chewed out.

00:14:53.092 --> 00:14:53.750
Chewed out?

00:14:55.113 --> 00:14:56.546
But at this point, I have to give in.

00:14:56.985 --> 00:14:58.682
My neck, back, and shoulders are killing me.

00:15:03.345 --> 00:15:04.703
Come here. I’ll give you a massage.

00:15:09.757 --> 00:15:11.047
Are you sure about this?

00:15:13.670 --> 00:15:14.331
Come on.

00:15:15.305 --> 00:15:15.955
Lie down over there.

00:16:23.739 --> 00:16:24.536
You.

