Hey, you're trembling. I can't do this right.

00:16:27.819 --> 00:16:29.245
It's because you're pressing too hard.

00:16:30.625 --> 00:16:31.750
I'm ticklish.

00:16:33.945 --> 00:16:35.315
Fine, I'll go easier then.

00:16:46.915 --> 00:16:48.165
Is this pressure okay?

00:16:58.985 --> 00:16:59.826
Yeah, that's actually pretty good.

00:17:42.065 --> 00:17:43.051
Feeling better?

00:17:44.465 --> 00:17:45.002
Yes.

00:17:50.585 --> 00:17:51.099
Let's go.

00:18:02.035 --> 00:18:02.835
Hello, Ken.

00:18:03.604 --> 00:18:05.305
Hey, did you just wake up?

00:18:05.615 --> 00:18:06.965
Yeah, I was on the night shift.

00:18:08.265 --> 00:18:11.585
Listen, I wanted to tell you that
Deputy Phakphum was in an accident yesterday.

00:18:11.910 --> 00:18:12.358
What?

00:18:13.945 --> 00:18:15.715
An accident? Where did it happen?

00:18:16.305 --> 00:18:17.840
