00:18:18.665 --> 00:18:19.785
He's in the hospital now.

00:18:21.185 --> 00:18:22.581
He should be fine now.

00:18:24.929 --> 00:18:26.463
I see.

00:18:26.745 --> 00:18:28.265
But based on the witness statements,

00:18:29.983 --> 00:18:31.451
I don't think it was an accident.

