It looked like a deliberate hit.

00:18:34.365 --> 00:18:35.325
Look into it for me.

00:18:35.785 --> 00:18:38.325
Ok. I'll head over and check
with the local precinct right away.

00:18:43.611 --> 00:18:47.638
I really can't tonight.
I have a VIP surgery case early tomorrow morning.

00:18:49.705 --> 00:18:51.409
But we haven't seen each other all week.

00:18:51.785 --> 00:18:52.915
I miss you so much.

00:18:55.329 --> 00:18:56.779
I miss you too.

00:18:57.524 --> 00:18:58.515
I have to go now.

00:18:58.945 --> 00:19:01.085
Okay, honey. Call me when you're done.

00:19:03.985 --> 00:19:05.085
I’m gonna barf.

00:19:06.715 --> 00:19:07.378
Dad.

