Not this again.

00:19:09.527 --> 00:19:11.812
I’m a grown man. Show me some respect.

00:19:12.945 --> 00:19:14.376
If you want my respect,

00:19:15.085 --> 00:19:17.082
then start acting like you deserve it.

00:19:18.063 --> 00:19:19.465
Are you talking to that girl again?

00:19:20.305 --> 00:19:23.558
