Does my talking to Ann benefit you in any way?

00:19:29.138 --> 00:19:29.875
Sir.

00:19:33.913 --> 00:19:34.545
What?

00:19:36.404 --> 00:19:37.868
That Phakphum. He survived.

00:19:42.905 --> 00:19:43.605
Please, come in.

00:19:44.303 --> 00:19:45.197
This way, please.

00:19:47.585 --> 00:19:48.485
Hello, sir.

00:19:49.138 --> 00:19:49.945
Hello, sir.

00:19:52.485 --> 00:19:53.802
- Hello, sir.
- Hello.

00:19:54.870 --> 00:19:55.525
Hello.

